{"title":"java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException解决方法","date":"2019-12-17T06:22:22.000Z","link":"post/362","tags":["java"],"categories":["java"],"updated":"2019-12-17T14:56:23.724Z","content":"<h1 id=\"错误原因\">错误原因<a href=\"post/362#错误原因\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">调用Arrays.asList()生产的List的add、remove、removeAll方法时报异常。</span><br><span class=\"line\">这是因为Arrays.asList() 返回的是Arrays的内部类ArrayList， 而不是java.util.ArrayList。</span><br><span class=\"line\">所以没有remove、add、rmoveAll方法，所以报错。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h1 id=\"解决方法\">解决方法<a href=\"post/362#解决方法\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"当Arrays-asList-生成list时，需要重新用一个new-ArrayList-来接受\">当Arrays.asList()生成list时，需要重新用一个new ArrayList()来接受<a href=\"post/362#当Arrays-asList-生成list时，需要重新用一个new-ArrayList-来接受\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    String[] array = &#123;&quot;1&quot;,&quot;2&quot;,&quot;3&quot;,&quot;4&quot;,&quot;5&quot;&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">List&lt;String&gt; list = Arrays.asList(array);</span><br><span class=\"line\">List arrList = new ArrayList(list);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"移除List中所有某个值","link":"post/363"},"next":{"title":"BootStrap Table 解决固定表头表头不对应","link":"post/359"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/362/","toc":[{"title":"错误原因","id":"错误原因","index":"1"},{"title":"解决方法","id":"解决方法","index":"2","children":[{"title":"当Arrays.asList()生成list时，需要重新用一个new ArrayList()来接受","id":"当Arrays-asList-生成list时，需要重新用一个new-ArrayList-来接受","index":"2.1"}]}]}